# ğŸ“ Yomito OCR

High-accuracy OCR library with **intelligent auto-optimization** for Python, powered by [Tesseract OCR](https://github.com/tesseract-ocr/tesseract).

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- ğŸŒ **Intelligent Language Detection** â€” automatic with multiple precision levels
- ğŸ”¤ **Multi-Language Support** â€” works with all Tesseract-compatible languages
- ğŸš **Flexible Modes** â€” `all`, `auto`, `auto_fast`, or manual language selection
- ğŸ¯ **High Accuracy** â€” preprocessing & optimization for better recognition
- âš¡ **Easy Integration** â€” simple Python API, ready to use

---

## ğŸ“¦ Installation

```bash
pip install yomito
```

### âš™ï¸ System Requirements

You need **Tesseract OCR** installed:

#### ğŸ§ Ubuntu/Debian
```bash
sudo apt-get install tesseract-ocr
sudo apt-get install tesseract-ocr-eng tesseract-ocr-rus tesseract-ocr-jpn
```

#### ğŸ macOS
```bash
brew install tesseract
brew install tesseract-lang
```

#### ğŸªŸ Windows  
